[% META
   title = "BMaster - Beekeeping Management System"
   description = "Beekeeping education, apiary management, queen rearing, bee health, and community resources"
%]
[% PageVersion = 'BMaster/BMaster.tt,v 0.03 2026/03/18 shanta Exp shanta' %]
[% IF debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

<div class="app-container">

    <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Welcome to BMaster</h1>
        <p class="page-subtitle">Your complete beekeeping management, education, and community platform.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-container">

        <div class="content-primary">

            [% UNLESS c.user_exists %]
            <div class="app-section">
                <h2>Getting Started</h2>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <p>New to BMaster or beekeeping? Follow this path to get the most out of the platform.</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li><strong>Create a free account</strong> — <a href="/user/create_account">Register now</a> to track your hives, save plants, and access member resources.</li>
                        <li><strong>Attend a workshop</strong> — <a href="/workshop">Browse upcoming hands-on sessions</a> led by experienced beekeepers.</li>
                        <li><strong>Set up your apiary</strong> — <a href="/BMaster/apiary">Start managing your hives and yards</a> in the Apiary Management System.</li>
                        <li><strong>Plan your forage</strong> — <a href="/ENCY/BeePastureView">Explore the Bee Pasture database</a> to ensure your bees have forage throughout the season.</li>
                    </ol>
                    <p>
                        <a href="/user/create_account" class="btn btn-primary">Create Your Free Account</a>
                        <a href="/workshop" class="btn btn-secondary">Browse Workshops</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            [% END %]

            <div class="app-section">
                <h2>Bee Pasture &amp; Forage Planning</h2>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <p>Diverse, year-round forage is the foundation of healthy, productive bees. Our Bee Pasture database catalogues hundreds of plants — noting their bloom time, nectar and pollen value, and suitability for different regions. Plan your garden or farm to ensure continuous forage from early spring through late autumn.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/ENCY/BeePastureView">Browse Bee Pasture Plants</a> — Filter by bloom season, nectar value, and more</li>
                        <li><a href="/ENCY/search">Search the Encyclopedia</a> — Find detailed plant profiles, insects, and forage guides</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><a href="/ENCY/BeePastureView" class="btn btn-primary">Open Bee Pasture Database</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="app-section">
                <h2>Hive and Apiary Management</h2>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <p>Run your beekeeping operation efficiently with our apiary management tools. Track yards, hives, and colonies. Monitor health, record inspections, and plan your season with confidence.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/BMaster/apiary">Apiary Management System</a> — Overview of your operation</li>
                        <li><a href="/BMaster/hive">Hive Management</a> — Track individual hive life and inspections</li>
                        <li><a href="/BMaster/beehealth">Bee Health Monitoring</a> — Disease, pests, and treatment tracking</li>
                        <li><a href="/BMaster/environment">Environmental Considerations</a> — Climate, forage, and site planning</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="app-section">
                <h2>Queen Rearing</h2>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <p>Raise quality queens with our dedicated queen rearing system. Plan grafting schedules, track emergence dates, and manage your mating nucleus colonies. A strong queen program is the foundation of a productive and gentle apiary.</p>
                    <p><a href="/BMaster/Queens" class="btn btn-primary">Queen Rearing System</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="app-section">
                <h2>Workshops and Learning</h2>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <p>Learn beekeeping in person and online. Our workshops range from introductory "first hive" sessions to advanced queen rearing and hive health intensives. Upcoming workshops are listed below — register to secure your spot.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/workshop">Browse All Workshops</a> — Upcoming and past sessions</li>
                        <li><a href="/BMaster/education">Education and Collaboration</a> — Online courses, tutorials, and study guides</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><a href="/workshop" class="btn btn-primary">See Upcoming Workshops</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="app-section">
                <h2>Honey Production</h2>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <p>Track honey harvests, extraction records, and production data across your operation. Learn best practices for harvesting, filtering, and storing quality honey for sale or personal use.</p>
                    <p><a href="/BMaster/honey" class="btn btn-primary">Honey Production</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="app-section">
                <h2>Community and Citizen Science</h2>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <p>BMaster is more than a management tool — it is a community of beekeepers contributing knowledge together. Members can contribute plant observations, pollen photos, and forage reports that benefit the entire community.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/ENCY/BeePastureView">Contribute plant forage data</a> — Share what is blooming in your area</li>
                        <li><a href="/ENCY/search">Explore community plant observations</a> — Benefit from what others have shared</li>
                    </ul>
                    [% UNLESS c.user_exists %]
                    <p><a href="/user/create_account" class="btn btn-primary">Join the Community</a></p>
                    [% END %]
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="app-section">
                <h2>Bee Products and Services</h2>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <p>Explore our range of bee products — from raw honey and beeswax to propolis and royal jelly. Members can advertise their own products and services to the beekeeping community.</p>
                    <p><a href="/BMaster/products" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Bee Products</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            [% IF c.check_user_roles('admin', 'developer') %]
            <div class="app-section admin-only">
                <h2>Management Tools</h2>
                <div class="content-section">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/BMaster/yards">Manage Yards</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/BMaster/add_yard">Add a New Yard</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            [% END %]

        </div>

        <div class="content-sidebar">

            [% UNLESS c.user_exists %]
            <div class="sidebar-section">
                <h4>Join BMaster</h4>
                <p>Create a free account to track your hives, save plants, register for workshops, and connect with the beekeeping community.</p>
                <p><a href="/user/create_account" class="btn btn-primary">Create Account</a></p>
            </div>
            [% END %]

            <div class="sidebar-section">
                <h4>Quick Links</h4>
                <ul class="sidebar-list">
                    <li><a href="/ENCY/BeePastureView">Bee Pasture Database</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/BMaster/apiary">Apiary Management</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/BMaster/Queens">Queen Rearing</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/workshop">Workshops</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/BMaster/beehealth">Bee Health</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/BMaster/honey">Honey Production</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/BMaster/education">Education</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/BMaster/products">Products &amp; Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/ENCY/search">Search Encyclopedia</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</div>
